wikipedia_page.main: Jei CanWin (known as Jei, J or Joe Ikhinmwin)  (born 18 September 1987) is a former British professional basketball player, who last played for the London Lions of the British Basketball League (BBL).

response: *London Lions' Joe Ikhinmwin won the annual BBL Slam Dunk Contest at Emirates Arena on 30 March.
In the 2019-20 season the Lions quickly resigned two-time BBL MVP Justin Robinson, Andre Lockhart and Lions captain Joe Ikhinmwin with the return of American forward Brandon Peel.
* On 14 July, 2020, the London Lions re-signed Captain Joe Ikhinmwin for the 2020–21 BBL season. This will be his eighth season with the Lions.
